马修·佩里的前女友担心他死前旧病复发https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perrys-ex-girlfriend-fears-he-suffered-relapse-before-death-3537559?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=matthew-perrys-ex-girlfriend-担心他死前复发Sam WarnerMon, 13 Nov 2023 12:11:57 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3537559 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马修·佩里" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “有很多事情对我来说不合时宜”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perrys-ex-girlfriend-fears-he-suffered-relapse-before-death-3537559">马修·佩里的前女友担心他死前旧病复发的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马修·佩里" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>马修·佩里的前女友分享了她对他死前旧病复发的担忧。</p><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/friends"><em>《老友记》</em></a>明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-dead-54-friends-tributes-3524335">上个月被发现死在洛杉矶的家中，享年 54 岁</a>，此后在一场私人葬礼上安息。</p><p>随后的毒理学报告发现，他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perrys-death-not-caused-by-meth-or-fentanyl-overdose-toxicology-report-confirms-3530056">死亡并非由甲基苯丙胺或芬太尼过量引起</a>，尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perrys-official-death-certificate-has-been-released-3536194">佩里的死亡证明</a>表明官方死因已“推迟”，初步尸检结果尚无定论。</p><p>凯蒂·爱德华兹 (Kayti Edwards) 曾与这位演员约会过，也曾担任过他的助理，她在一次新的采访中表示，过去曾与毒瘾作斗争的佩里可能在他去世前一周复发了。 </p><figure id="attachment_3537605" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3537605" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3537605" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1.jpg" alt="马修·佩里" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3537605" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年 4 月 22 日星期六，加利福尼亚州洛杉矶，马修·佩里 (Matthew Perry) 在南加州大学举行的第 28 届洛杉矶时报年度图书节上与马特·布伦南 (Matt Brennan) 谈论他的书。图片来源：盖蒂 / 丹尼亚·麦克斯韦</figcaption></figure><p>“有很多事情对我来说不合时宜，”她告诉<a href="https://www.thesun.co.uk/tvandshowbiz/24707413/matthew-perry-ex-girlfriend-prescription-pill-relapse-fears/?utm_source=sharebar_app&amp;utm_medium=sharebar_app&amp;utm_campaign=sharebar_app_article" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>太阳报</em></a>。 “我不相信他只是淹死在他的按摩浴缸里，这听起来不对。我认识马修，我也知道他不会淹死。</p><p> “我认为他可能在这之前的一周内服用了药物。他们说现场没有处方止痛药，这并不令我感到惊讶，因为他没有在周围留下药物。</p><p> “他很偏执，会把所有的东西都拿走，所以没有任何证据，然后当他准备好时就出去拿更多的东西。”</p><p>爱德华兹还指出，佩里在去世前的最后一篇社交媒体帖子中使用了“马特曼”这个头衔，并解释说：“马特曼的事情不是他清醒时做的。马特曼在不清醒的时候就会出来，他感觉有点无敌。</p><p> “当他兴奋时我就在场，尽管我并没有和他一起兴奋，当我说也许他应该用药物来冷静一点时，他会说，‘不，我是马特曼’。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cyuv2zDrL0r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.88