92" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IsqqjOxEuAg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>本周末有报道称这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-thomas-anderson-has-reportedly-worked-with-radiohead-spin-off-the-smile-on-new-project-3537196">传奇导演与乐队合作制作了</a>一部新视频。吉他手格林伍德此前曾为安德森的电影<i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/licorice-pizza-review-alana-haim-3105747#:~:text=%27Licorice%20Pizza%27%20review%3A%20a,life%20topped%20with%20Alana%20Haim&amp;text=Casting%20two%20people%20who%27ve,spicy%20moves%20for%20decades%20now.">《甘草披萨》</a> 、《血色将至》</i>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/the-movies-blog/the-master-the-years-finest-film-782559"><em>《大师》</em></a>配乐。</p><p> 《Wall Of Eyes》是他们 2022 年首张唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-smile-a-light-for-attracting-attention-radiohead-thom-yorke-jonny-greenwood-3222308">A Light For Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attracting Attention</a> 》的后续作品。新专辑由 Oxford 和 Abbey Road Studios 录制，并由之前的合作者 Sam Petts-Davies 制作和混音。它还具有伦敦当代管弦乐团的弦乐编曲。</p><p>在下面找到专辑封面和曲目列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3537586" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3537586" style="width: 1920px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3537586" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-smile-wall-of-eyes-album-art.jpeg" alt="斯坦利·唐伍德 (Stanley Donwood) 和汤姆·约克 (Thom Yorke) 创作的《眼墙》艺术作品" width="1920" height="1920" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-smile-wall-of-eyes-album-art.jpeg 1920w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-smile-wall-of-eyes-album-art-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-smile-wall-of-eyes-album-art-400x400.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-smile-wall-of-eyes-album-art-800x800.