news/mortal-kombat-1-homelander-wont-be-voiced-by-the-boys-star-3537529">不会</a>由<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/the-boys">男孩</a></em>演员安东尼·斯塔尔配音。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/modern-warfare-3-manager-says-reports-of-rushed-development-are-wholly-inaccurate-3537585">《现代战争 3》的负责人表示，有关仓促开发的报道“完全不准确”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
